    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞称人工智能 iPhone 前景不乐观，苹果股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/apple-dips-as-jefferies-says-hopes-for-ai-phone-are-overblown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 股价下跌 2.3%，此前杰富瑞 (Jefferies) 的一位分析师表示，投资者对该公司最新款 iPhone（首款配备人工智能工具的 iPhone）的预期过于乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/apple-dips-as-jefferies-says-hopes-for-ai-phone-are-overblown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 14:22:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富国银行警告亚马逊云计算业务“实力不足” 股价遭下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-cut-as-wells-fargo-warns-cloud-strength-not-enough</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司 (Amazon.com Inc.) 股价周一下跌，此前分析师罕见下调其评级，理由是担心明年的利润率趋势，而云计算业务的增长不太可能弥补这一影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-cut-as-wells-fargo-warns-cloud-strength-not-enough</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
